Package com.im.njams.sdk.communication

Interface ShareableReceiver<M>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - The raw message type that is received from the transport API
    All Superinterfaces:
    Receiver
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SharedHttpSseReceiver, SharedJmsReceiver, SharedKafkaReceiver
    public interface ShareableReceiver<M>
extends Receiver
    Interface to be implemented by Receivers that support receiving messages for multiple Njams instances.
    Author:
    cwinkler
